description:
Gaze upon the stars and other celestial bodies. Experience the most beautiful sights and learn even more with Sorthern Sky Map. Travel through our Solar System or stroll along the Southern and Northern sky. Your journey into space starts now!

Key Features:

- A picture book aesthetic
- Interactive learning experience
- Nonlinear exploration
- An adorable kitten
- You can even pet her!
- Relaxing music
name: Southern Sky Map
